channel.title: Help with server
channel.description:
So i've had a working server. and it worked perfectly. and now i have this error Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: Gui Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: Gui at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) Could not find the main class: Gui. Program will exit. Press any key to continue . . .
And i tried redownloading the source and client. and it still doesn't work i still get the same error but please help me

item.title: Help with server
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

[quote=“rich1716, post:8, topic:426216”]oh ok in my source or client? well this is my client one

@echo off
title Client
cd ./Class/
“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe” -Xmx500m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
pause[/quote]

Replace yours with this:

@echo off
title Client
cd ./Class/
"C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe" -Xmx500m -cp .; Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
pause

Let us know how it works.

Read full topic
